data.title: Eternity PLUS
data.meta_description: Eternity is an angelic sky blue cream shade. Important details - 12ml bottle- Extra long wear nail polish (no curing required) - can last up to 2 weeks- Strengthens and hydrates the nails- Smooths the appearance of ridges- Self levelling formula- High gloss- Quick dry- 2 coat coverage- Plant based, vegan and cruelty fr
data.text:
All I Scream Nails PLUS polishes are made in Australia

I Scream Nails PLUS nail polish is free of the following:

Formaldehyde, Tosylamide Formaldehyde Resin & Ethyl Tosylamide, Toluene, Dibutyl Phthalate, Xylene, Triphenyl Phosphate, Camphor, Animal by-products and animal derived ingredients, Benzophenones, Styrene acrylates
